data.description: Discover this versatile 4-bedroom, 1 and ¾ bathroom home designed for comfortable living and endless possibilities.     Natural light floods the bright, open living areas, creating an inviting atmosphere throughout.     With unique features like two full kitchens and a converted garage, this home offers flexibility for various lifestyles, whether accommodating guests or creating a functional home office. MORE PIX COMING SOON. Nestled in a coveted neighborhood with an unbeatable location, this residence provides easy access to major highways and excellent shopping options just a short drive away.  Please note, recent enhancements including the enclosed back patio, additional kitchen, bathroom and garage were not permitted but offers added space, functionality and further utility to this adaptable home.  Washer, Dryer and TV mounts do not convey!  Ample parking in the driveway and on the street.   Stay tuned for more pictures coming soon to fully appreciate all this home has to offer!
